# ACGS Multi-Agent Guidelines
Constitutional Hash: cdd01ef066bc6cf2

## Core Rules
- Validate hash `cdd01ef066bc6cf2` in all operations
- P99 <5ms latency, >85% cache hit, >100 RPS
- FastAPI + Pydantic v2 + async/await only
- O(1) lookups with caching

## Architecture
- Claude: Strategic planning, compliance, MCP
- OpenCode: Execution, files, testing
- Hierarchy: Orchestrator → Specialist → Worker

## Services
- ACGS: Auth 8016, AI 8001, Coord 8008, Board 8010
- MCP: Agg 3000, FS 3001, Git 3002, Browser 3003
- DB: PostgreSQL 5439, Cache: Redis 6389

## Libraries
- Agents: Pydantic AI (no LangChain)
- Comms: MCP for Claude
- Test: pytest-asyncio
- Monitor: Prometheus

## Anti-Patterns
- No sync in async
- No direct agent comms without validation
- No hardcoded URLs/hash
- No custom auth (use 8016)

## Targets
- Latency: P99 <5ms
- Throughput: >100 RPS
- Cache: >85%
- Compliance: 100%
